                        <p part="N">卷軸</p>
                        <decoNote>
                                    The handscroll with wide borders (大鑲手卷) showcases a protective and decorative backing (錦包首) 
                                    crafted from pale-blue silk, bearing signs of fading and staining. The 'Heaven' section (天) is 
                                    elegantly fashioned from pale-blue silk. Vertical stripes (隔水) exhibit a blend of white and 
                                    pale-blue silk. The borders are skillfully made of white silk. The frontispiece (引首) and colophon 
                                    section (拖尾) are crafted from traditional Chinese paper, showing delicate signs of staining. 
                                    Unfortunately, the silken cord and toggle are missing.
                                    大鑲手卷，天為淡藍色有花紋絲織物，有磨損和褪色痕跡。副隔水為白色有花紋絲織物，隔水為淡藍色絲織物。引首為白色紙本，
                                    拖尾為白色紙本，略有污跡。邊為白色絲織物。錦包首為藍綠色絲織物伴有紅色花紋，八寶帶和別子已遺失，題簽為黃色紙本。</decoNote>
